      "link"			: "http://hywel.github.io/blog/a-phonetic-post/",
      "excerpt"		: "<p>I am now testing the work flow to see how the phonetic fonts are rendered and check unicode compliance.</p>

<ul>
  <li>/θɪs ɪs eɪ pɐʉst wɪθ ə fɔˈnɛtɪk ˈkɔmpɐʉnənt/</li>
  <li>This is a post with a phonetic componant</li>
</ul>

<p><img src="/figures/spectrogram1.png" alt="Spectrogram" /></p>

<h2 id="diacritics">Diacritics</h2>
<ul>
  <li>Diacritics are often a problem</li>
  <li>pʰɜt̪o</li>
  <li>Rə̄</li>
  <li>Su̺ <sup id="fnref:1"><a href="#fn:1" class="footnote">1</a></sup></li>
</ul>

<p>All of the diacritics seem to render correctly <sup id="fnref:2"><a href="#fn:2" class="footnote">2</a></sup>. I will check them along the way.</p>

<p>Below I will embed an audio file from <a href="http://www.soundcloud.com">soundcloud</a>.</p>

